snippet.description:
Get Katam👇👇👇
https://dplatnumz.lnk.to/katam

"KATAM" is a sweet, catchy love anthem that brings together two East African powerhouses—Diamond Platnumz and @BienOfficial in a celebration of beauty, love, and unity across the continent. The song produced by S2Kizzy is all about that one special woman who leaves you completely speechless—her vibe, her shape, her roots—everything about her is katam tam, meaning irresistibly sweet. Through playful lyrics and smooth harmonies, Diamond and Bien paint a picture of a woman whose charm reflects the richness of East Africa—from her Rwandan glow, Somali hair, Ethiopian eyes, to her Tanzanian sweetness and Kenyan smarts. It's flirty, fun, and full of pride—an Afro-pop jam that makes you want to dance, fall in love, and raise a toast to all the beautiful queens of Africa."

snippet.title: Mbosso - Pawa (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Music video by Mbosso performing, “Pawa” (Power), is a heartfelt, poetic love song by Mbosso that captures the overwhelming power of deep affection. Using rich metaphors and smooth vocals, he likens love to an intoxicating force that leaves him weak and emotionally charged — “naishiwa pawa” (I’m losing power). The lyrics blend vulnerability with admiration, painting his lover as a source of strength and inspiration. With a melodic blend of Bongo Flava and soulful instrumentation, “Pawa” showcases Mbosso’s lyrical depth and emotive style. The music was shot in Iringa, Tanzania, Directed by Folex & Audio produced by S2Kizzy.

snippet.title: Iyanii ft Dufla Diligon - Donjo Maber (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Iyanii returns with a high-energy banger, teaming up with the ever-vibrant Dancehall maestro Dufla Diligon to deliver “Donjo Maber” — a pulsating track built to get you on your feet.

Infused with infectious beats and rhythmic grooves, Donjo Maber is a celebration of Luo culture, seamlessly blended with a fresh Afro Dancehall vibe. The song bridges tradition and modernity, showcasing Iyanii’s unique ability to fuse cultural identity with mainstream appeal.

This marks the third official release from Iyanii’s highly anticipated upcoming album, and it’s a clear indication that he’s not holding back. With a catchy hook, dynamic energy, and undeniable chemistry between the two artists, Donjo Maber is poised to be a favorite on dance floors and playlists across the region.
